<item>
            <title>[SPARK-3782] Direct use of log4j in AkkaUtils interferes with certain logging configurations </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3782</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AkkaUtils is calling setLevel on Logger from log4j. This causes issues when using another implementation of SLF4J such as logback as log4j-over-slf4j.jars implementation of this class does not contain this method on Logger.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
